properties.areaDesc: Death Valley National Park; Western Mojave Desert
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 10 at 10:04AM PST until February 11 at 4:00AM PST by NWS Las Vegas NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph are
possible.

* WHERE...Death Valley National Park and Western Mojave Desert.

* WHEN...Until 4 AM PST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
Some areas of blowing dust will be possible as well, reducing
driving visibility.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM PST TUESDAY
